room_title: Escape room "The Haunting" by Escape Tuscaloosa in Tuscaloosa
room_description: In an abandoned haven on the North side of town, you can hear the whispers of the past and the souls amongst the living. Between the blood on the walls, the cracks in the floor and the chill in the air, this place has a story – and it’s a gruesome one. Many things have made this place home; be cautious not to disturb their personal possessions or sacred space – nothing makes them angrier! With Halloween around the corner, do you dare enter? And if you do, can you escape?!
